------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation of software for Broadcom 2835 
RPi General Purpose Input Output (GPIO) via Broadcom 2835
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

References: 
-----------

https://raspberrypi.stackexchange.com/questions/81757/why-and-when-to-use-rpi-gpio-vs-bcm2835

http://www.spazztech.com/python-vs-c-on-rpi.html

http://www.airspayce.com/mikem/bcm2835/

Instructions: 
-------------

[1] download the most recent version of bcm2835-*.tar.gz ... e.g., 
    http://www.airspayce.com/mikem/bcm2835/bcm2835-1.73.tar.gz 
     ... to ~/Code/Data-Aq/RPi-DataAq

[2] tar zxvf bcm2835-1.73.tar.gz
    cd bcm2835-1.73
    ./configure
    make
    sudo make check
    sudo make install
    cd ..
    rm -rf bcm2835-1.73

------------------------------------------------------------------------------


